https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/nSbCcELd9FfigN0O7ZuVr8TQIOL.jpg 2 Rats is a 2003 Nigerian comedy film directed by Andy Chukwu. Nollywood's highest-paid actors, Osita Iheme and Chinedu Ikedieze, play two young boys whose father has been murdered by their uncle. In a selfish move, Amaechi Muonagor wants them to work as house boys in their father's own house. 2 Rats
